                            <h3 style="color:#7045af" id="PlanName">  樂活銀髮方案<input id="PlanID" type="hidden"  name="PlanID" value="2"/> </h3>
                                
                            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush ">
                                <li class="list-group-item"><strong style="color:#b1297d">價格</strong>: NT$</li>
